OL,3,CFire expert critical of Summerland but
OL,4,Cdoes not see it as 'an injustice'
OL,6,FThe last surviving member of the
OL,7,FSummerland fire research team says the
OL,8,F'misadventure' ruling given to those
OL,9,Fwho died in 1973 is a "strange
OL,10,Fverdict".
OL,12,FJohn Webb was part of a team of
OL,13,Fexperts who went into the building on
OL,14,Fthe Isle of Man four days after the
OL,15,Ffire, working with a team from the
OL,16,FFire Research Station in 1973 to find
OL,17,Fthe cause of the blaze.
