OL,3,CFire expert critical of Summerland but
OL,4,Cdoes not see it as 'an injustice'
OL,6,FWhile taking photographs of what
OL,7,Fremained of the building, the team
OL,8,Fdiscovered that a key piece of
OL,9,Fevidence was missing.
OL,11,FJohn said: "Basically it is us
OL,12,Ffollowing the trail of the fire and
OL,13,Fwhy it spread so rapidly.
OL,15,F"There were no detailed drawings into
OL,16,Fhow the site was constructed because
OL,17,Fit had been changed at the last
OL,18,Fminute".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
