OL,3,CFire expert critical of Summerland but
OL,4,Cdoes not see it as 'an injustice'
OL,6,FIn his view, the factors that led to
OL,7,Fthe tragedy were vast, and the issues
OL,8,Fstarted with the original design.
OL,10,F"There were a lack of escape routes
OL,11,Fand lack of staff training. They
OL,12,Fshould have sounded the alarm when the
OL,13,Ffire was first spotted and clearing
OL,14,Fthe building", John said.
OL,16,FA commission into the fire was
OL,17,Fpublished just six months after the
OL,18,Fdisaster and included findings from
OL,19,FJohn's team, yet he was surprised, the
OL,20,Fconclusions led to little
OL,21,Faccountability.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
