OL,3,CFire expert critical of Summerland but
OL,4,Cdoes not see it as 'an injustice'
OL,6,FHe said: "I understand that the
OL,7,Fsurvivors and families of survivors
OL,8,Ffeel the misadventure verdict
OL,9,Fcondemned their families and friends
OL,10,Fwho died because they went into a
OL,11,Fbuilding that wasn't apparently safe.
OL,13,F"If that's what the coroner meant,
OL,14,Fthat is a very strange verdict.
OL,15,FLooking back I can only be astonished
OL,16,Fthat only 50 people died".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
