OL,3,CFire expert critical of Summerland but
OL,4,Cdoes not see it as 'an injustice'
OL,6,FThe former fire officer was critical
OL,7,Fof the building materials used at the
OL,8,Ftime, and questioned how much training
OL,9,Fwas given to the staff but he wouldn't
OL,10,Fdescribe the fire as an 'injustice'.
OL,12,F"We are all looking back with
OL,13,Fhindsight, with a much greater
OL,14,Fknowledge of what building materials
OL,15,Fdo and a lack of training when the
OL,16,Fbuilding was in use", he said.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
