OL,3,CFire expert critical of Summerland but
OL,4,Cdoes not see it as 'an injustice'
OL,6,FThe disaster, which occurred on 2
OL,7,FAugust 1973, was started by three
OL,8,Fyoung boys who were smoking in a
OL,9,Fdisused kiosk, up against the main
OL,10,FSummerland complex.
OL,12,FA total of 50 people died, and 80 more
OL,13,Fwere seriously injured, after the fire
OL,14,Fspread through the island's leisure
OL,15,Fcomplex.
